<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Electro-Bills | Certified Electrical Engineers</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
  margin:0;
  padding:0;
  box-sizing:border-box;
  font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
  scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

body{
  background:#0a0f1a;
  color:#fff;
}

/* NAVBAR */
nav{
  position:fixed;
  top:0;
  width:100%;
  background:rgba(10,15,26,0.9);
  backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items:center;
  padding:15px 30px;
  z-index:1000;
  border-bottom:1px solid #222;
}

nav h1{
  color:#ffd000;
  font-size:20px;
}

nav a{
  color:#ccc;
  margin-left:15px;
  text-decoration:none;
  font-size:14px;
}

nav a:hover{
  color:#ffd000;
}

/* HERO */
.hero{
  height:100vh;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  justify-content:center;
  align-items:center;
  text-align:center;
  padding:20px;
  background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.7),rgba(0,0,0,0.9)),
  url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621905252507-b35492cc74b4') center/cover;
}

.hero h2{
  font-size:55px;
  color:#ffd000;
  animation:fadeIn 1.5s ease;
}

.hero p{
  max-width:600px;
  margin-top:10px;
  color:#ddd;
}

.btn{
  margin-top:25px;
  padding:12px 22px;
  background:#ffd000;
  color:#000;
  font-weight:600;
  border-radius:8px;
  text-decoration:none;
  transition:0.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
  transform:scale(1.05);
}

/* SECTIONS */
section{
  padding:80px 20px;
  max-width:1100px;
  margin:auto;
}

h3.title{
  text-align:center;
  color:#ffd000;
  font-size:28px;
  margin-bottom:40px;
}

/* GRID */
.grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
  gap:20px;
}

.card{
  background:#121a2a;
  padding:20px;
  border-radius:12px;
  border:1px solid #222;
  transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover{
  transform:translateY(-5px);
  border-color:#ffd000;
}

.card h4{
  color:#ffd000;
  margin-bottom:10px;
}

/* PRICING */
.price{
  text-align:center;
  font-size:22px;
  color:#ffd000;
}

/* FAQ */
.faq{
  background:#121a2a;
  margin-bottom:10px;
  padding:15px;
  border-radius:8px;
  cursor:pointer;
}

.faq p{
  display:none;
  margin-top:10px;
  color:#ccc;
}

/* CONTACT */
form{
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  gap:10px;
}

input, textarea{
  padding:12px;
  border:none;
  border-radius:6px;
  outline:none;
}

textarea{
  resize:none;
  height:120px;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer{
  text-align:center;
  padding:20px;
  background:#070b12;
  color:#888;
}

/* WHATSAPP FLOAT */
.whatsapp{
  position:fixed;
  bottom:20px;
  right:20px;
  background:#25D366;
  padding:15px;
  border-radius:50px;
  font-size:20px;
  text-decoration:none;
  color:#fff;
}

/* ANIMATION */
@keyframes fadeIn{
  from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(-20px);}
  to{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<nav>
  <h1>⚡ Electro-Bills</h1>
  <div>
    <a href="#services">Services</a>
    <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <h2>Certified Electrical Engineers</h2>
  <p>Safe, Reliable & Professional Electrical Services for Homes, Businesses & Industrial Projects in Nigeria.</p>
  <a class="btn" href="https://wa.me/234XXXXXXXXXX">Get Free Quote</a>
</div>

<section id="services">
  <h3 class="title">Our Services</h3>

  <div class="grid">

    <div class="card">
      <h4>House Wiring</h4>
      <p>Complete wiring installation for new and old buildings.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Fault Detection</h4>
      <p>Fast troubleshooting and repair of electrical issues.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Solar Systems</h4>
      <p>Installation of modern solar power systems.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Inverter Setup</h4>
      <p>Backup power solutions for homes and offices.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section id="pricing">
  <h3 class="title">Simple Pricing</h3>
  <div class="card">
    <p class="price">Inspection: ₦5,000 – ₦10,000</p>
    <p class="price">House Wiring: From ₦80,000</p>
    <p class="price">Solar Installation: Custom Quote</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h3 class="title">FAQ</h3>

  <div class="faq">Do you work outside Abuja?
    <p>Yes, we handle projects across Nigeria depending on scale.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq">Do you offer emergency services?
    <p>Yes, we respond to urgent electrical faults quickly.</p>
  </div>

</section>

<section id="contact">
  <h3 class="title">Contact Us</h3>

  <form>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name">
    <input type="text" placeholder="Phone Number">
    <textarea placeholder="Describe your project..."></textarea>
    <button class="btn" type="submit">Send Message</button>
  </form>

  <br>

  <iframe 
    src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18..."
    width="100%" height="250" style="border:0;border-radius:10px;">
  </iframe>

</section>

<footer>
  © 2026 Electro-Bills Electrical Services | Built for professionals
</footer>

<a class="whatsapp" href="https://wa.me/234XXXXXXXXXX">💬</a>

<script>
document.querySelectorAll(".faq").forEach(faq=>{
  faq.addEventListener("click",()=>{
    let p = faq.querySelector("p");
    p.style.display = p.style.display === "block" ? "none" : "block";
  });
});
</script>

</body>
</html>
